text: Geumdaebong is a mountain in the province of Gangwon-do, in South Korea. Its area extends over the cities of Taebaek, Samcheok and the county of Jeongseon. Geumdaebong has an elevation of .An 2007, p.90. ==See also== * List of mountains in Korea ==Notes== ==References== * Category:Mountains of South Korea Category:Mountains of Gangwon Province, South Korea Category:One- thousanders of South Korea zh:金台峰
